---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div id="continuity-journey" class="bg-gray-50 py-24 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <Container>
    <div class="space-y-16">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">From chaos to continuity</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
          Clarify how work really happens so AI can land with confidence
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          We help operations leaders evolve from inconsistent execution and siloed knowledge to a shared, well-governed operating model that is ready for automation and intelligent tooling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <section class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-lg shadow-primary/5 dark:bg-gray-950">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Current state reality</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Processes run differently across teams, creating unpredictable outcomes and unreliable data.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Accountability is fuzzy, handoffs stall progress, and “pass the parcel” ownership erodes trust.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Continuity planning lives with a few people, leaving critical knowledge scattered and fragile.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Change communication is inconsistent, documentation is dated, and initiatives stop-start—driving up cost.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-lg shadow-primary/5 dark:bg-gray-950">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Target operating state</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span><span>Standardised processes generate predictable data, enabling faster, better-informed decisions.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span><span>Clear lines of authority accelerate delivery, reduce meetings, and unblock approvals.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span><span>Up-to-date process assets remain accessible during PTO, transitions, or attrition.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span><span>Planned change is captured in one place so everyone knows what’s happening and who to contact.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>


    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
